    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The engine and transmission are functional, though you may notice some minor fluid seepage and the suspension feels a bit soft over bumps. Visually, the paint has some fading and there are noticeable scuffs on the bumpers, while the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery and some cracked plastic trim. It is a solid, drivable car that would benefit from a dedicated owner to address these minor cosmetic and mechanical maintenance items.",
