    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It has been such a reliable companion and is still in great shape for its next big adventure! It\u2019s been well-loved, kept clean, and runs like a dream, making it absolutely perfect for your daily commutes or fun weekend getaways. I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make its next owner very happy. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. This unit features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. The chassis is structurally sound with documented rear subframe reinforcement and a recent VANOS system service to ensure timing precision. The suspension utilizes a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup, currently fitted with refreshed bushings for precise turn-in. While the exterior shows minor stone chips and patina consistent with spirited use, the drivetrain is dialed in and the compression across all cylinders remains within factory tolerances. A purist\u2019s specification ready for the B-roads.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Regular maintenance performed. Clean title. Reliable daily driver. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between daily reliability and premium comfort. The exterior maintains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only minor signs of careful use consistent with its age. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the leather upholstery is supple with minimal wear on the driver\u2019s bolster, and every button, switch, and digital display functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car has been fastidiously maintained with a complete service history available for review. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. It sits on a set of premium tires with plenty of tread remaining. Whether you are commuting or taking a long road trip, this car offers a dependable, high-quality driving experience that has been clearly cared for by its previous owner.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning motorist seeking a synthesis of reliability and sophisticated performance. Exhibiting a consistent service history and exceptional structural integrity, the automobile delivers a refined driving experience that aligns with our dealership's rigorous standards for quality. We invite you to inspect this distinguished example of engineering excellence, which offers significant value for those who prioritize both provenance and prestige.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
