      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolute gold for me. It\u2019s been super well-loved and is running like a dream\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road. I\u2019ve kept up with the maintenance, so it's totally ready for its next adventure with you! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself, you're going to love it!",
      "price": 29500.0,
