      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver\u2019s specimen featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual and a limited-slip variable M differential. Critical preventative maintenance is addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement. The suspension geometry remains tight with upgraded poly-bushings, and the braking system utilizes cross-drilled rotors for superior heat dissipation. While showing minor aerodynamic stone chips and interior wear consistent with its mileage, its mechanical integrity and power delivery remain sharp.",
